---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Games | 唐靖凯" description="主机游戏体验与推荐">
  <section class="section glass" style="max-width: 900px;">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>Games</h2>
      <p>主机游戏体验与推荐。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="metrics">
      <div>
        <h4>平台</h4>
        <p>PS5 / Switch / Steam Deck</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>类型偏好</h4>
        <p>JRPG / 类魂 / 肉鸽 / 剧情向</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>态度</h4>
        <p>白金/全成就不是目的，体验才是。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-grid" style="margin-top: 24px;">
      <article class="project-card">
        <h3>占位：游戏评测与短评</h3>
        <p>准备开始记录：玩过的游戏、通关感想、推荐与避坑。</p>
        <span>Ongoing / Reviews</span>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
